# 4. Just declaring a Cash account should not disable the fallback
# regexp for Asset accounts.
<
account assets        ; 
account assets:cash   ; type:Cash

2021-01-01
  (assets)       1
  (assets:cash)  1

$ hledger -f- bs -N
